'''大卫·格雷伯'''（{{lang-en|David Graeber}}，{{bd|1961年|2月12日|2020年|9月2日|catIdx=Graeber}}），[[美国|美国]][[人类学家|人类学家]]，[[无政府主义|无政府主义]]活动家。[[倫敦政治經濟學院|倫敦政治經濟學院]]教授<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lse.ac.uk/anthropology/people/departmentalstaff.aspx|title=London School of Economics Department of Anthropology Staff List|publisher=[[倫敦政治經濟學院|London School of Economics]]|accessdate=2013-09-30|archive-date=2017-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171029225141/http://www.lse.ac.uk/anthropology/people/departmentalstaff.aspx|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。以对[[官僚主义|官僚主义]]、政治和[[资本主义|资本主义]]的尖锐描写而闻名<ref>{{cite web |author1=吴俊燊 |author2=董牧孜 |title=占领华尔街运动发起人、人类学家大卫·格雷伯逝世，享年59岁 |url=http://www.bjnews.com.cn/culture/2020/09/04/765632.html |publisher=[[新京报|新京报]] |date=2020-09-04}}</ref>。

== 生平 ==
他的父母是[[工人阶级|工人阶级]]出身的知识分子<ref name=businessweek/>，且都是[[犹太人|犹太人]]<ref>{{cite web|author=Stuart Jeffries|date=2015-03-21|url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2015/mar/21/books-interview-david-graeber-the-utopia-of-rules|title=David Graeber interview: So many people spend their working lives doing jobs they think are unnecessary|work=The Guardian|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2020-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200909074139/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2015/mar/21/books-interview-david-graeber-the-utopia-of-rules?paging=off|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他的母亲露丝·鲁宾斯坦曾是一名制衣工人，1930年代活跃于国际妇女服装工人工会，并在音乐剧中扮演主要角色<ref name=businessweek/><ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2006/04/20/classified/paid-notice-deaths-graeber-ruth-r.html |title=Paid Notice: Deaths: Graeber, Ruth R. |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |date=2006-04-20 |accessdate=2011-12-04 |archive-date=2018-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180729083115/https://www.nytimes.com/2006/04/20/classified/paid-notice-deaths-graeber-ruth-r.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他的父亲肯尼斯早年加入[[美国青年共产主义联盟|美国青年共产主义联盟]]，参加了1936年[[巴塞罗那|巴塞罗那]]的西班牙革命和[[西班牙内战|内战]]。1939年[[苏德互不侵犯条约|苏德签订互不侵犯条约]]前便退出了青年联盟<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.alba-valb.org/volunteers/kenneth-graeber |publisher=Abraham Lincoln Brigade: Spanish Civil War History and Education |title=Kenneth Graeber |accessdate=2011-12-04 |archive-date=2012-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107063238/http://www.alba-valb.org/volunteers/kenneth-graeber/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

大卫·格雷伯于1978年毕业于[[菲利普斯学院|菲利普斯学院]]，1984年获纽约州立大学帕切斯分校文学学士学位。后在[[芝加哥大学|芝加哥大学]]深造，期间获得[[富布赖特项目|富布赖特奖学金]]，在[[马达加斯加|马达加斯加]][[贝塔富|贝塔富]]进行了为期20个月的[[民族誌研究|民族誌研究]]和[[田野調查|田野調查]]<ref name=Berrett>{{cite news |last=Berrett |first=Dan |title=Intellectual Roots of Wall St. Protest Lie in Academe |date=2011-10-16 |newspaper=The Chronicle of Higher Education |url=http://chronicle.com/article/Intellectual-Roots-of-Wall/129428/ |accessdate=2013-02-19 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407092538/https://chronicle.com/article/Intellectual-Roots-of-Wall/129428/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1996年获博士学位，其博士论文《1987年的灾难：马达加斯加农村地区的记忆与暴行》，导师为[[馬歇爾·薩林斯|馬歇爾·薩林斯]]<ref name=arenson/><ref name="YaleBio">{{cite web |last=Graeber |first=David |title=David Graeber |website=Yale University Department of Anthropology |publisher=Yale University |year=2004 |url=http://www.yale.edu/anthropology/people/dgraeber.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040222235548/http://www.yale.edu/anthropology/people/dgraeber.html |archivedate=2004-02-22 |access-date=2020-09-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

1998年，受聘为[[耶鲁大学|耶鲁大学]]助教授，随后升任副教授<ref name=arenson/>。2005年5月，在他即将获得[[终身教授|终身教职]]的前一年，耶鲁大学人类学系决定不与他续约。格雷伯指责这是由于[[政治立场|政治立场]]原因。有4500多名同事和学生在支持他的请愿书上签名<ref name=arenson>{{cite news|last=Arenson|first=Karen W.|title=When Scholarship and Politics Collided at Yale|url=https://www.nytimes.com/2005/12/28/nyregion/28anarchist.html?pagewanted=all|accessdate=2011-12-04|work=The New York Times|date=2005-12-28|archive-date=2012-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120323170809/http://www.nytimes.com/2005/12/28/nyregion/28anarchist.html?pagewanted=all|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2005年12月，他同意在接受一年的带薪休假后离开耶鲁大学。2006年春，他教了最后两门课程“文化人类学导论”（有200多名学生参加）和“直接行动和激进社会理论”研讨会。2008年至2013年，他在[[倫敦大學金匠學院|倫敦大學金匠學院]]任教。2013年，他接受了[[伦敦政治经济学院|伦敦政治经济学院]]的教授职位<ref>{{cite news|last=Shea|first=Christopher|title=A Radical Anthropologist Finds Himself in Academic 'Exile'|url=http://chronicle.com/article/A-Radical-Anthropologist-Finds/138499/|accessdate=2013-04-15|newspaper=Chronicle of Higher Education|date=2013-04-15|archive-date=2013-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130417105924/http://chronicle.com/article/A-Radical-Anthropologist-Finds/138499/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

[[File:NLN_David_Graeber.jpg|thumb]]移民者集会]]

20世纪90年代后期，他开始积极参与政治活动。他是2011年[[佔領華爾街|佔領華爾街]]运动的关键人物之一。2011年11月，《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》杂志称赞格雷伯为占领华尔街运动提供了主题“[[我們就是那99%的人|我們就是那99%的人]]”。但是格雷伯却说，这个[[口号|口号]]“是大家集体创造的”<ref>{{cite book|last=Graeber|first=David|title=The Democracy Project|url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_9780812993561/page/41|page=41|quote=As a matter of historical record, since there is so much discussion of the origin of the slogan "We Are the 99 Percent," the answer is that - appropriately enough - it was a collective creation.|publisher=Spiegel & Grau|date=2013|ISBN=978-0812993561}}</ref>。2011年8月2日，他参与召集第一届纽约市大会，当时仅有60名参与者。随后，他参加工作组会议以及组织有关非暴力抵抗的法律和医学培训班。他曾在[[祖科蒂公园|祖科蒂公园]]扎营数天，后离开纽约市前往[[得克萨斯州|得克萨斯州]][[奥斯汀|奥斯汀]]<ref name=businessweek>{{cite news|last=Bennett|first=Drake|title=David Graeber, the Anti-Leader of Occupy Wall Street: Meet the anthropologist, activist, and anarchist who helped transform a hapless rally into a global protest movement|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2011-10-27/anthropologist-graeber-turns-radical-side-loose-in-zuccotti-park|accessdate=2011-12-04|newspaper=[[Business_Week|Business Week]]|date=2011-10-26|archive-date=2020-08-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200822101012/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2015/mar/21/books-interview-david-graeber-the-utopia-of-rules|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年10月11日，格雷伯在伦敦[[特拉法加廣場|特拉法加廣場]]的[[反抗滅絕|反抗滅絕]]活动中发表讲话，谈到“狗屁工作”与环境损害之间的关系<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.timeout.com/london/theatre/writers-marathon-by-writers-rebel|title=Writers Marathon by Writers Rebel | Theatre in London|website=Time Out London|accessdate=2020-09-04|archive-date=2019-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191012120735/https://www.timeout.com/london/theatre/writers-marathon-by-writers-rebel|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年，他与妮卡·杜布罗夫斯基（Nika Dubrovsky）结婚<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://twitter.com/davidgraeber/status/1121332583630016512/|title=I've never been married before. Even though the proper ceremony is later in London & Berlin, I have never been more moved that someone who actually knows me would want to be with me forever.|author=David Graeber|via=Twitter|date=25 April 2020|access-date=12 September 2020|archive-date=2020-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903195209/https://twitter.com/davidgraeber/status/1121332583630016512|url-status=no}}</ref>。2020年9月2日他在意大利[[威尼斯|威尼斯]]与妻子和朋友一起度假时，因[[急性胰腺炎|急性胰腺炎]]在当地的一家医院去世，享年59岁<ref name=Guardian>{{cite news |author=Cain, Sian |title=David Graeber, anthropologist and author of Bullshit Jobs, dies aged 59 |date=2020-09-03 |accessdate=2020-09-03 |work=The Guardian |url=https://www.theguardian.com/books/2020/sep/03/david-graeber-anthropologist-and-author-of-bullshit-jobs-dies-aged-59 |archive-date=2020-09-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200903155214/https://www.theguardian.com/books/2020/sep/03/david-graeber-anthropologist-and-author-of-bullshit-jobs-dies-aged-59 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在生前的最后一刻，依然像往常一样活跃于[[Twitter|Twitter]]<ref>{{cite web |title=自述：我是怎样成为一个无政府主义者的 |url=https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_9025830 |publisher=澎湃新闻 |date=2020-09-04 |access-date=2020-09-04 |archive-date=2020-12-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201226182352/https://www.thepaper.cn/newsDetail_forward_9025830 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

